  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "SD Gundam Gaiden: Knight Gundam Monogatari 2 - Hikari no Knight is a Role-Playing game, developed by TOSE and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 1991.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "Knight Gundam and other heroes defeated the Black Dragon, and there was a brief moment of peace. However, after learning of the true ruler's existence, Knight Gundam departed once again. The other hero who fought with him also set out on a journey of training...",
